{"tid":2370394,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"祭品食家李薇 被發現用長者八達通發難","createTime":"2021-01-18T04:13:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T07:02:56.000Z","uid":364041,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cd76d26fd2873d67667bdac4ee0c5dedf43f284f","tid":2370394,"uid":364041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T04:13:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/961241340592601/posts/3862147687168604/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F961241340592601%2Fposts%2F3862147687168604%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS%2Fo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=6cb6b478\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/961241340592601/posts/3862147687168604/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【咁大件事冇人講？】中大政政系助理教授李薇，早前食用二手祭品，以節儉成名。<br />\n<br />\n這兩天在公務員secrets及公海流出片段，一名女士在深水埗站被職員查獲使用長者卡，其後發難，並且失控尖叫，狀甚哀慟。有政政同學向本社透露，片中正是李薇老師，而由她昨天fb的帖文可見，的確曾身處深水埗區，眼鏡亦同款。<br />\n<br />\n片中李教授重覆「做乜嘢」、「做乜嘢」，又解釋自己是「用錯咗八達通」。本社相信李教授並非無心之失，也不是食用祭品鬼上身，而是以長者卡對抗港鐵霸權，盡量唔益黨鐵，而失聲尖叫象徵着對吃人政權控訴，不平則嗌，竭力發聲。對於她棄共投明的舉動，本社深表敬佩，建議大家一人一信寄中大，表揚她的行為。<br />\n<br />\nMeWe：<a href=\"https://mewe.com/p/潮文社\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmewe.com%2Fp%2F%E6%BD%AE%E6%96%87%E7%A4%BE&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS%2Fo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=dab30d0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mewe.com/p/潮文社</a><br />\nFB：<a href=\"https://www.fb.me/9.Literature/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fb.me%2F9.Literature%2F&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS%2Fo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=e66548af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.fb.me/9.Literature/</a><br />\nIG：<a href=\"https://instagram.com/9.literature\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2F9.literature&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS%2Fo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=cba0314d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/9.literature</a>"},{"pid":"d18669c4b99427efd37c92fdd7ab9eae986f47c2","tid":2370394,"uid":326287,"lik